```cpp

#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
#define int long long
#define LL long long
#define PII pair<int, int>
#define map unordered_map
#define x first
#define y second
#define endl "\n"
#define debug(x) cout << #x << ' ' << x << endl;
const int N = 110;
int n, m;
int s[N];
int v[N][N], w[N][N];
int dp[N];
signed main()
{
    // freopen(".in", "r", stdin);
    ios::sync_with_stdio(0);
    cin.tie(0);
    cin >> n >> m;
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
    {
        cin >> s[i];
        for (int j = 1; j <= s[i]; j++)
        {
            cin >> v[i][j] >> w[i][j];
        }
    }
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
        for (int j = m; j >= 0; j--)
            for (int k = 0; k <= s[i]; k++)
                if (j - v[i][k] >= 0)
                    dp[j] = max(dp[j], dp[j - v[i][k]] + w[i][k]);
                else
                    continue;
    cout << dp[m];
    return 0;
}
```
